I"V<p><a href="http://rolandtanglao.com/2020/07/29/p1-blogthis-checkvist-list-links-to-blog/">Discovered</a>: Nov 27, 2024 20:08 <a href="https://www.bannerbear.com/blog/how-to-convert-audio-to-video-for-youtube-upload-using-ffmpeg/#convert-mp3-to-mp4-with-an-image">How to Convert Audio to Video for Youtube Upload Using FFmpeg - Bannerbear</a> &lt;– this worked with a 256x256px image! –&gt; <strong>QUOTE</strong>: <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">ffmpeg -loop 1 -i image.jpg -i input.mp3 -c:v libx264 -vf "pad=ceil(iw/2)*2:ceil(ih/2)*2" -shortest output_image.mp4</code></p>
